TITLE: Canceling Vercel Blob Uploads with AbortController (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the new abortSignal option with an AbortController to cancel ongoing Vercel Blob upload requests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/storage/blob/main/test/next/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-08_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const abortController = new AbortController();

vercelBlob
  .put('canceled.txt', 'test', {
    access: 'public',
    abortSignal: abortController.signal,
  })
  .then((blob) => {
    console.log('Blob created:', blob);
  });

setTimeout(function () {
  // Abort the upload
  abortController.abort();
}, 100);
```

